  "detailed_description": "Terix Survivors is a time survival game with minimalistic gameplay and roguelite elements.<br />\r\nHell is empty, the devils are here, and there's no place to run or hide.<br />\r\nAll you can do is survive as long as you can until death inevitably puts an end to your struggles. <br />\r\nGather gold in each run to buy upgrades and help the next survivor.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe supernatural indie phenomenon that lets you be the bullet hell!",
